text: Samia Hachemi (سامية•هاشمي; born 19 June 1966) is an Algerian judoka. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, where judo was for women a demonstration sport, in the weight event. She competed at the 1986 African Judo Championships where she won the bronze medal in the -66 kg category. == References == Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Algerian judoka
